  "description": [
    "The California Eagle Thursday January 20 1949 8 AIRLINES AGENCY LAUNCHED prominent Los Angeles businessman is pictured signing the final documents that officially launched the first airline agency operated by a member of his race on the Pacific Coast Operating under the name Airlines Service the com pany will offer air line service to all sections of the nation at economic and moderate cost to air travelers Seated at the right Mrs Yvonne Shelton will be in charge of ticket sales at the office of Airlines Service located at 4108 South Central Avenue In the center Betty Mann a plane travel executive witnesses the official start of the pioneer business another progressive step by McClain AFL Sponsors Committee Formed to Rid Strikers Organization of an American Federation of Labor Sponsors 1 Committee to Aid the Kress Strikers was announced this XWeek by the Acting Chairman ofj the Committee Mr Claude Mc Guinn Secretary Treasurer of 1 he Dining Car Employees Local jfnion No 582 Other Union officials who have Accepted membership on the Xommittee are Mrs James M 3Vhite President and Mr L B Thompson Secretary Treasurer pf the Los Angeles Division of the International Brotherhood of Sleeping Car Porters"
